{
  "stem": "2004.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, our temple-- we belonged to the temple which was in the Czech side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was really very easy for us to cross over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All we need is a yearly passport for which we paid a relatively small fee, and we could just go as many times, communicate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We could walk over the bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The town, being a small town, was relatively easy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So from the place where we lived-- from the apartment house that we lived to the apartment house where my relatives lived on the Czech side was approximately maybe a 15 to 20 minutes walk.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we took advantage of it, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we-- the family was close family, and we saw each other every day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was an only son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Basically, I was an only son because I had a older-- I had an older brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My older brother died shortly after I was born.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I believe I was a year old when my brother died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was during an diphtheria epidemic at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I was born in 1927, and my understanding is that he has died in 1928.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I attended public school in my hometown of Cieszyn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was also a member of a Zionist organization, of a Zionist youth organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was known as the Betar at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was very, very social.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, we were-- we were learning the virtues of the Jewish homeland, of the future Jewish homeland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Furthermore, it was also well organized because we had-- we had outings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We played a lot of ping pong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it gave us something to do, so to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the revisionistic organization of the Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe that is now the Likud.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
